.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# ── Ingested data ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# books/ and db/ are committed ON PURPOSE so a fresh clone on any device already
# has the ingested books + vector DB — no need to re-ingest. Only the per-user
# accounts DB and the rendered page-image cache stay out of git.
db/users.db
static/book_images/

